Date: Wed, 21 Aug 2024 14:16:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 78/95] NVIDIA: SAUCE: virt: tegra: build tegra_hv.c driver as
 built-in driver

skip building tegra_hv driver for oot kernel from
nvidia-oot repo and start building with oot kernel
as inbuild driver to improve boot KPI.

http://nvbugs/4551265

